<https://nielshoffmann.github.io/bblock-dcat-ap-nl/> a skos:ConceptScheme,
        dcat:Catalog,
        bblocks:BBlocksRegister ;
    rdfs:label "Building Blocks - OGC Building Blocks for DCAT-AP-NL 3.0 - EXPERIMENTAL" ;
    dct:abstract """These building blocks are an experimental implementation of DCAT-AP-NL.
"""^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
    dct:description """The purpose of this collection is to experiment with the building block approach and to showcase how
this potentially can add value.

Note: the building blocks in the geonovum repository are a more conservative implementation while the 
building blocks in this repository are more experimental.
"""^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
